Rattlesnake Canyon



We took a hike in Rattlesnake Canyon, at the other end of the campsite, looking for a spring that was supposed to be there, but some dry washes distracted us and we ended up finding this interesting slick white rock formation instead.
Taken Saturday, October 12, 2002, 03:25:17pm.  Original image size: 3072x1728, 7.7Mb
